org.apache.flink.yarn

类 YarnResourceManagerCallbackHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.yarn.YarnResourceManagerCallbackHandler
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    org.apache.hadoop.yarn.client.api.async.AMRMClientAsync.CallbackHandler

    public class YarnResourceManagerCallbackHandler
extends Object
implements org.apache.hadoop.yarn.client.api.async.AMRMClientAsync.CallbackHandler
    This class reacts to callbacks from the YARN Resource Manager. In order to preserve actor concurrency safety, this class simply sends corresponding messages to the Yarn resource master actor.
